C%20and%20sleep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20Devlin%20Donaldson%20was%20preparing%20for%20an%20early%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20busy%20CEO%20of%20a%20nonprofit%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehad%20suffered%20a%20stroke%20in%202018.%20That's%20how%20he%20discovered%20he'd%20already%20been%20living%20with%20type%202%20diabetes%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20diagnosis%2C%20things%20didn't%20change%20much.%20Despite%20bouncing%20around%20from%20medication%20to%20medication%2C%20and%20listening%20to%20%26quot%3Buninspiring%26quot%3B%20diet%20advice%20from%20a%20nutritionist%2C%20his%20health%20was%20not%20improving%2C%20and%20his%20blood%20sugar%20was%20out%20of%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20I%20went%20to%20my%20doctor%2C%20it%20was%20like%2C%20'well%2C%20that's%20not%20working%2C'%20here's%20another%20prescription%2C%20here's%20another%20prescription%2C%26quot%3B%20Donaldson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAt%20some%20point%2C%20I%20just%20sort%20of%20lost%20hope%2C%20and%20I%20said%2C%20'Forget%20it.%20I'm%20just%20going%20to%20die%20young.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20was%20pretty%20skeptical%20when%20he%20signed%20up%20to%20try%20out%20a%20digital%20%26quot%3Btwin%26quot%3B%20designed%20to%20improve%20his%20condition%20and%20help%20him%20slash%20his%20stack%20of%20medications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20a%20digital%20twin%20is%20just%20an%20app%20full%20of%20advice%20on%20how%20to%20eat%20and%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20Donaldson%20said%2C%20the%20personalized%20insights%20transformed%20his%20understanding%20of%20his%20body%2C%20and%20the%20challenges%20he%20faced.%20Three%20years%20later%2C%20his%20diabetes%20is%20in%20remission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf3dda96-8995-4af2-82e0-af94242eaa6c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Digital%20twin'%20tech%20is%20a%20fast-growing%20type%20of%20precision%20medicine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CGM%20on%20a%20man's%20arm%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664f5953a961b37edf392d02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwin%20gives%20users%20continuous%20glucose%20monitors%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20scale%20that%20measures%20body%20composition%2C%20a%20smartwatch%2C%20and%20a%20blood%20pressure%20cuff.%3Cp%3EHalfpoint%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarket.us%2Freport%2Fdigital-twins-in-healthcare-market%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPersonalized%2520Healthcare%2520Solutions%2Cimproving%2520patient%2520experiences.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDigital%20twins%20in%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20being%20used%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-a-longevity-clinic-executive-physical-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elongevity%20clinics%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20in%20hospitals.%20They%20can%20track%20a%20patient's%20health%20over%20time%2C%20suggesting%20personalized%20interventions.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20optimize%20treatment%20plans%2C%20making%20them%20more%20compatible%20with%20each%20person's%20unique%20preferences%20and%20biology.%20It's%20a%20type%20of%20precision%20medicine%20that's%20growing%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDonaldson%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20customers%20at%20Twin%20Health.%20Twin%20Health%20is%20the%20only%20company%20that%20leverages%20digital%20twin%20AI%20for%20diabetes%20%26quot%3Breversal%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20as%20doctors%20prefer%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3Bremission.%26quot%3B%20Competitors%20like%20Virta%20Health%20and%20Omada%20don't%20place%20as%20much%20emphasis%20on%20individualizing%20their%20diabetes%20reversal%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDonaldson%20was%20a%20reluctant%20participant%20in%20the%20program%20at%20first.%20%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20super%20enthusiastic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20to%20get%20my%20hopes%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20since%20it%20was%20free%20%E2%80%94%20paid%20for%20through%20his%20employer's%20healthcare%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20he%20tried%20it%20out.%20(Some%20employers%20require%20patients%20with%20diabetes%20to%20use%20Twin%20to%20get%20their%20prescriptions%20covered.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20he%20couldn't%20help%20feeling%20at%20least%20a%20little%20intrigued%20by%20Twin's%20promise%20of%20healing.%20This%20wasn't%20about%20managing%20his%20disease%3B%20they%20were%20going%20to%20try%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20his%20diabetes%2C%20or%20so%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20understanding%20was%20diabetes%20was%20something%20you%20lived%20with%20for%20your%20whole%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20got%20it%2C%20you%20had%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwin%20sent%20a%20box%20to%20his%20home%20that%20included%20a%20digital%20scale%2C%20a%20blood%20pressure%20cuff%2C%20a%20smartwatch%2C%20and%20a%20continuous%20glucose%20monitor%20(CGM)%20to%20track%20how%20different%20foods%20and%20activities%20impacted%20his%20blood%20sugar%20levels%20throughout%20the%20day.%20Then%20his%20%26quot%3Btwin%26quot%3B%20settled%20in%20and%20got%20to%20work%2C%20noticing%20patterns%20in%20his%20routines%20and%20measuring%20his%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c928e4f-ce5d-4f0e-86f1-9c636cdd96cb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorking%20with%20the%20'twin'%20involves%20logging%20food%2C%20and%20getting%20regular%20exercise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222119%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hiking%20person%20legs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664f619f239fda2da6caf284%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221415%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGajus%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20a%20twin%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20misnomer%2C%20really.%20Donaldson%20says%20his%20%26quot%3Btwin%26quot%3B%20is%20much%20more%20like%20a%20dashboard%20he%20can%20check%20to%20get%20advice%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fhigh-protein-fiber-pancakes-man-lost-weight-reversed-diabetes-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20foods%20are%20best%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20eat%20when%2C%20or%20how%20he's%20doing%20with%20his%20steps%20goal.%20It%20also%20monitors%20his%20medications%2C%20glucose%20levels%2C%20and%20blood%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20manually%20enters%20everything%20he%20eats%2C%20which%20is%20arduous%20but%20enlightening%2C%20he%20said.%20If%20his%20blood%20sugar%20starts%20going%20up%2C%20he's%20noticed%20that%20getting%20out%20for%20a%20walk%20can%20help%20bring%20it%20back%20down.%20He%20knows%20his%20body%20reacts%20better%20when%20he%20starts%20eating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-tips-man-lost-40-pounds-10-inches-walking-nutrients-order-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehis%20veggies%20before%20the%20protein%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20meal%2C%20feeding%20his%20stomach%20a%20base%20of%20some%20fiber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221047%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22screenshot%20of%20twin%20app%20showing%20blood%20glucose%20spike%20after%20'orange'%20meal%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664e249a14fb5b23cc5f2978%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221575%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Twin%20app%20pairs%20advice%20with%20feedback%20from%20a%20smartwatch%2C%20a%20continuous%20glucose%20monitor%2C%20a%20digital%20scale%2C%20and%20a%20blood%20pressure%20cuff.%20%3Cp%3ETwin%20Health%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20becomes%20very%20much%20about%20my%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20my%20information%20goes%20in%20and%20it%20talks%20to%20me%20like%20a%20smarter%20version%20of%20myself%20saying%2C%20'you%20ate%20this%2C%20this%20was%20really%20good.%20You%20ate%20this%2C%20this%20was%20really%20bad.'%20And%20it%20begins%20to%20give%20me%20this%20feedback%20cycle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegistered%20dietician%20Nicola%20Guess%2C%20who%20studies%20the%20prevention%20and%20management%20of%20type%202%20diabetes%20at%20Oxford%20University%2C%20and%20who%20is%20not%20involved%20with%20Twin%2C%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bpleasantly%20surprised%26quot%3B%20with%20how%20the%20system%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20where%20tech%20can%20be%20so%20useful%2C%26quot%3B%20Guess%20said.%20While%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6HT4lAI5_x%2F%3Fhl%3Den%26img_index%3D2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe's%20generally%20not%20a%20fan%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20people%20with%20normal%20blood%20sugar%20using%20CGMs%20(because%20there's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-weight-loss-12-pounds-spiking-increasing-blood-sugar-levels-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Every%20little%20the%20CGM%20can%20tell%20us%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20metabolic%20health%20of%20non-diabetic%20patients)%20she%20said%20the%20way%20Donaldson%20uses%20his%20CGM%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20true%3A%20if%20you%20have%20type%202%20diabetes%2C%20your%20excursions%2C%20your%20glucose%20can%20cause%20you%20to%20go%20blind%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20people%20feel%20empowered%20by%20being%20able%20to%20real-time%20check%20on%20what%20that%20is%2C%20I%20get%20that%20completely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20more%20than%20what%20an%20Apple%20Watch%20or%20a%20Fitbit%20would%20do.%20In%20addition%20to%20data%20from%20the%20CGM%2C%20there%20are%20regular%20blood%20pressure%20cuff%20readings%20and%20the%20bathroom%20scale%20measures%20his%20body%20composition.%20Donaldson%20can%20also%20ask%20his%20Twin%20questions%20while%20he's%20on%20the%20go%2C%20like%20when%20he%20showed%20up%20to%20a%20work%20event%20where%20they%20were%20only%20serving%2