ted%20to%20other%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20weather%2C%20low%20population%20density%2C%20safety%2C%20economy%2C%20education%20opportunities%2C%20taxes%2C%20and%20a%20first-class%20healthcare%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2.%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dubai%2C%20UAE%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664f5f3c20abc1efe8fce1e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDubai%2C%20UAE%3Cp%3EAnadolu%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2023%20estimated%20net%20gain%20of%20millionaires%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%204%2C500%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2022%20net%20gain%20of%20millionaires%20(rank)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%205%2C200%20(1)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%2C%20the%20number%20of%20net%20new%20millionaires%20in%20the%20UAE%20has%20quadrupled%20from%20its%20pre-pandemic%20levels%20of%20about%201%2C000%20annually.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20recent%20growth%20also%20coincides%20with%20EXPO%202020%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20World%20Expo%2C%20where%20nations%20and%20millions%20of%20visitors%20gathered%20to%20look%20for%20solutions%20to%20issues%20the%20world%20is%20facing.%20This%20event%20is%20credited%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhfre.ae%2Fblog%2Finternational-investors-attract-to-dubais-safe-haven-status%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eputting%20the%20UAE%20on%20the%20international%20map%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmoils%20described%20the%20UAE%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bforemost%20wealth%20hub%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%26quot%3B%20and%20credits%20its%20attractiveness%20to%20factors%20such%20as%20its%20safe%20haven%20status%2C%20diverse%20economy%20across%20several%20key%20sectors%2C%20low%20taxes%2C%20luxury%20real%20estate%2C%20good%20schools%2C%20and%20a%20top%20healthcare%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20millionaires%20moving%20to%20the%20UAE%20come%20from