ess-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-seeks-cci-approval-for-8-5-bn-viacom18-star-india-merger-124052500702_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-seeks-cci-approval-for-8-5-bn-viacom18-star-india-merger-124052500702_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Was%20Chandrayaan-3%20Touchdown%20Spot%20Named%20'Shiv%20Shakti'%3F%20PM%20Modi%20Explains%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20explained%20why%20the%20government%20named%20the%20spot%20on%20the%20Moon%20where%20India's%20Chandrayaan-3%20lander%20Vikram%20touched%20down%20as%20'Shiv%20Shakti'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2023%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation's%20Chandrayaan-3%20Vikram%20lander%20successfully%20touched%20down%20on%20the%20dark%20side%20of%20the%20Moon%20near%20the%20south%20pole.%20The%20Pragyaan%20rover%20onboard%20the%20lander%20rolled%20down%20and%20left%20imprints%20of%20the%20national%20emblem%20on%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20addressed%20ISRO%20scientists%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20named%20the%20spot%20'Shiv%20Shakti'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20why%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20named%20it%20'Shiv%20Shakti'%20and%20not%20something%20else%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20could've%20been%20named%20something%20else.%20If%20they%20(Opposition)%20were%20in%20power%2C%20they%20would've%20named%20it%20after%20their%20family...but%20I%20cannot%20do%20that.%20India%20has%20given%20a%20philosophy%20to%20the%20world%20and%20I%20feel%20proud%20in%20naming%20it%20after%20the%20idea%20which%20controls%20the%20universe%20(Shiv%20Shakti).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20say%20'Shiv%20Shakti'%2C%20140%20crore%20people%20of%20India%20can%20connect%20with%20it.%20If%20a%20family%20had%20named%20it%2C%20then%20only%20a%20section%20of%20the%20population%20could%20connect%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShiv%20Shakti%20is%20a%20name%20that%20motivates%20and%20empowers.%20It%20is%20a%20name%20that%20guides%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20reacted%20to%20the%20Opposition's%20allegation%20of%20%26quot%3Bcalling%20the%20government's%20accomplishments%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20first%20issue%20is%20whether%20we%20are%20proud%20of%20India's%20achievements%20or%20not%2C%20and%20whether%20should%20we%20do%20it%20or%20not.%20I%20don't%20understand%20why%20they%20have%20a%20problem%20in%20feeling%20proud%20of%20the%20accomplishment.%20They%20say%20why%20does%20Modi%20take%20credit%3F%20Instead%20of%20feeling%20proud%2C%20they%20want%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee's%20government%20was%20in%20power%2C%20we%20detonated%20the%20nuclear%20bombs%20in%201998.%20The%20Opposition%20said%20the%20scientists%20had%20done%20it.%20Thirteen%20days%20later%2C%20India%20detonated%20another%20bomb%20despite%20facing%20sanctions%2C%20there%20was%20the%20political%20will%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Chandrayaan-2%20failed%20in%202019%2C%20there%20was%20strength%20in%20the%20political%20leadership%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20the%20failure%20by%20standing%20next%20to%20the%20scientists.%20I%20could've%20run%20away%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20do%20it%20and%20stayed%20there%20to%20motivate%20them.%20I%20take%20ownership%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716628740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fnfr1e7v8_pm-modi-interview-ndtv_625x300_24_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-explain