20policies%2C%20or%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20state%20entirely.%20The%20state-backed%20Citizens%20Property%20Insurance%20Corporation%20is%20now%20the%20top%20underwriter%20as%20private%20companies%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20a%20look%20at%20the%20ground-breaking%20Hunters%20Point%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Hunters%20Point%20community%20sits%20on%20a%20bay%20separated%20from%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20by%20a%20barrier%20island.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222652%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20Hunter's%20Point%20development%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66476d3b9fc063e829b2434a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20aerial%20view%20of%20the%20Hunters%20Point%20development%20in%20Cortez%2C%20Florida.%20%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Hunters%20Point%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECortez%2C%20Florida%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20Hunters%20Point%20development%20is%20located%20%E2%80%94%20is%20known%20for%20its%20white-sand%20beaches%20and%20historic%20fishing%20villages.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20tiny%20town%20of%20over%204%2C000%20residents%2C%20Cortez%20is%20an%20hour%20south%20of%20Tampa%2C%20near%20Bradenton%20Beach%2C%20a%20popular%20vacation%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHunters%20Point%20developer%20Marshall%20Gobuty%20challenged%20his%20team%20to%20build%20homes%20that%20were%20both%20net-zero%20and%20LEED-certified.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hunters%20Point%20homes%20under%20construction%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66476e2114fb5b23cc5db77a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHunters%20Point%20and%20nearby%20Palma%20Sola%20Bay.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Hunters%20Point%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20residential%20homes%20have%20been%20left%20behind%20in%20the%20push%20to%20build%20LEED-certified%2C%20sustainable%20developments%2C%20Gobuty%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20museums%20and%20commercial%20buildings%2C%20but%20residential%20is%20really%20like%20a%20step-sister.%20It's%20not%20been%20traditionally%20dominant%20for%20LEED%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELEED%20is%20a%20certification%20developed%20by%20the%20nonprofit%20US%20Green%20Building%20Council%20that%20verifies%20a%20building's%20sustainable%20design%20and%20efficient%20energy%20use%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usgbc.org%2Fleed%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Green%20Building%20Council%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Net-zero%20means%20the%20the%20amount%20of%20energy%20a%20building%20consumes%20is%20equal%20to%20the%20amount%20of%20energy%20it%20produces%20through%20renewable%20means%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.energy.gov%2Fsites%2Fprod%2Ffiles%2F2015%2F09%2Ff26%2FA%2520Common%2520Definition%2520for%2520Zero%2520Energy%2520Buildings.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20the%20federal%20government%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGobuty's%20team%20built%20the%20first%20prototype%20home%20in%20a%20warehouse.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20shot%20of%20a%20row%20of%20Hunters%20Point%20homes%20right%20on%20the%20water%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66476e2320abc1efe8fb046d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHomes%20at%20Hunters%20Point.%20%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Hunters%20Point%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20observed%20the%20prototype%20over%2018%20months%20in%20conditions%20that%20recreated%20the%20changing%20seasons%20before%20starting%20construction%20in%20the%20real%20world.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGobuty%20was%20able%20to%20develop%20homes%20that%20actually%20produce%20more%20energy%20than%20they%20consume.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20Hunters%20Point%20homes%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66476e2214fb5b23cc5db77d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221526%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESolar%20panels%20on%20top%20of%20homes%20at%20Hunters%20Point.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Hunters%20Point%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGobuty%20decided%20he%20wanted%20the%20homes%20to%20use%20a%20mix%20of%20solar%20and%20battery%20energy%2C%20choosing%20the%20German%20startup%20sonnenBatterie%20to%20provide%20the%20units%20to%20power%20the%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20generating%2035%25%20more%20power%20than%20we%20modeled%20and%20we're%20consuming%2025%25%20less%2C%26quot%3B%20Gobuty%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBetter%20insulation%20also%20helps%20the%20homes%20conserve%20energy.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20Hunters%20Point%20homes%20from%20the%20front%20gate%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66476e219fc063e829b24535%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20patio%20on%20a%20Hunters%20Point%20property%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Hunters%20Point%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGobuty%20explained%20his%20team%20used%202%C3%976%20insulation%20boards%20for%20the%20Hunters%20Point%20homes%20instead%20of%20the%20typical%202%C3%974.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20creates%20resiliency%2C%20strength%2C%20and%20as%20well%20keeps%20this%20envelope%20tight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20when%20Hunters%20Point%20conducted%20industry-standard%20%26quot%3Bblower%20door%26quot%3B%20tests%2C%20a%20diagnostic%20tool%20to%20see%20how%20much%20air%20escapes%20the%20home%2C%20they%20tested%20tighter%20than%20the%20established%20rating%20system%2C%20Gobuty%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGobut