%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilt%20as%20a%20railway%20hotel%2C%20the%20Balmoral%20is%20home%20to%20a%20clock%20tower%20that's%20become%20a%20staple%20of%20the%20city's%20skyline.%20Balmoral%20staff%20seem%20to%20love%20to%20note%20that%20the%20clock%20is%20almost%20never%20right%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it's%20set%20three%20minutes%20ahead%20to%20help%20travelers%20make%20their%20trains.%20It's%20only%20right%20on%20New%20Year's%20Eve%20(for%20obvious%20celebratory%20reasons).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hotel%20has%20hosted%20several%20of%20Britain's%20VIPs%2C%20from%20Paul%20McCartney%20to%20J.K.%20Rowling.%20In%202007%2C%20Rowling%20finished%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%20and%20the%20Deathly%20Hallows%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20final%20installment%20of%20the%20wizarding%20series%2C%20at%20the%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20suite%20marked%20with%20a%20bright%20purple%20door%20is%20now%20named%20after%20the%20author.%20If%20the%20room%20has%20suffered%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjk-rowling-transgender-comments-show-reality-wizarding-world-harry-potter-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERowling's%20recent%20controversies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20doesn't%20show%3A%20On%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20hotel%2C%20I%20was%20told%20the%20suite%20is%20regularly%20rented%20out%20%E2%80%94%20for%20around%20%244%2C000%20a%20night.%20It%20was%20booked%20for%20the%20entirety%20of%20my%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20hotel%20reopened%20after%20a%20massive%20refurbishment%20in%20the%20'90s%2C%20Sean%20Connery%20cut%20the%20ribbon%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20Now%2C%20bathrooms%20throughout%20the%20hotel%20are%20fitted%20with%20playful%20prints%20of%20the%20first%20James%20Bond%20actor.%20(Mine%2C%20which%20hangs%20across%20from%20the%20bathroom's%20heated%20towel%20rack%2C%20is%20of%20Bond%20playing%20poker%20with%20an%20eye-patched%20villain.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20suite%20in%20the%20Balmoral%20Hotel%2C%20overlooking%20Edinburgh's%20Sir%20Walter%20Scott%20monument.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66503d0fa961b37edf398f04%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20suite%20in%20the%20Balmoral%20Hotel%2C%20overlooking%20Edinburgh's%20Sir%20Walter%20Scott%20monument.%3Cp%3EJordan%20Parker%20Erb%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20its%20history%2C%20the%20Balmoral%20doesn't%20feel%20stuffy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20thanks%20to%20Olga%20Polizzi%2C%20the%20deputy%20chairman%20and%20director%20of%20design%20at%20Rocco%20Forte%20Hotels.%20Tasked%20with%20designing%20spaces%20across%20the%20Rocco%20Forte%20portfolio%2C%20Polizzi%20has%20ensured%20that%20rooms%20match%20the%20vibe%20of%20the%20city%20in%20which%20they're%20based.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Balmoral's%20case%2C%20that%20meant%20creating%20a%20cottage-like%20retreat%20in%20the%20city's%20center.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hotel's%20thoughtfully%20curated%20rooms%20feel%20like%20they%20belong%20in%20a%20countryside%20estate.%20Floral%20wallpaper%20and%20pillows%20marked%20with%20woodland%20creatures%20draw%20inspiration%20from%20the%20natural%20world%2C%20while%20tartan%20textiles%20give%20the%20hotel%20a%20distinctly%20Scottish%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20make%20no%20mistake%3A%20For%20as%20quaint%20and%20cozy%20as%20the%20rooms%20feel%2C%20they're%20not%20constricting.%20Soaring%20ceilings%20help%20the%20already%20large%20rooms%20feel%20even%20bigger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20that%20the%20homey%20rooms%20are%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20hole%20up%20for%20a%20rainy%20weekend%20in%20Edinburgh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbalmoral-hotel-rocco-forte-edinburgh-scotland-review-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716627841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66503