%2C%20but%20it%20sucked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2279e058af-178e-4bf8-bb38-75c8305bac6b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EJob%20searching%20is%20a%20full-time%20role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20thought%20was%20that%20finding%20another%20job%20at%20this%20age%20and%20stage%20in%20my%20career%20would%20be%20difficult.%20The%20older%20you%20are%20when%20you%20get%20laid%20off%2C%20the%20harder%20it%20is%20to%20find%20an%20equivalent%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20a%20break%20to%20clear%20my%20head%20and%20started%20my%20job%20search%20in%20January.%20I%20updated%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20looked%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20Indeed%2C%20and%20job%20posting%20apps.%20From%20Sunday%20to%20Tuesday%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20time%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20I%20spend%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%20researching%20and%20applying%20for%20jobs.%20I%20treat%20it%20like%20a%20day%20job.%20Then%2C%20I%20take%20a%20few%20days%20off%2C%20which%20keeps%20me%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-cant-get-hired-remote-jobs-tech-sales-layoffs-health-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapplying%20to%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20Portland%2C%20where%20I%20live%2C%20and%20some%20remote%20jobs%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20found%20a%20few%20jobs%20that%20are%20very%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20I%20had.%20Half%20a%20dozen%20times%2C%20I%20spent%20two%20hours%20tailoring%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20to%20a%20job%2C%20showing%20how%20my%20qualifications%20directly%20matched%20the%20role%20and%20then%20got%20back%20an%20auto-generated%20rejection%20response%20within%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20frustrating.%20Some%20days%2C%20I've%20felt%20a%20little%20defeated.%20But%20I%20have%20to%20remind%20myself%20it's%20not%20a%20human%20at%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20line.%20It's%20probably%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290d129b5-6ba0-48ca-b18f-fa92446bc0b8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20applied%20for%20400