%20as%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdifferences-day-care-between-us-germany-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emy%20kids'%20classmates%20and%20friends%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20can't%20name%20a%20single%20child%20born%20in%20recent%20years%20whose%20name%20falls%20into%20this%20category.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20wildly%20popular%20name%20Luca%20is%20a%20top%2010%20name%20for%20boys%20in%20Germany%20right%20now%2C%20and%20I%20know%20dozens%20of%20little%20Luca's.%20While%20theoretically%2C%20%26quot%3BLuca%26quot%3B%20is%20allowed%20to%20be%20used%20for%20girls%20as%20well%2C%20I%20have%20yet%20to%20meet%20a%20single%20female%20Luca.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20my%20kids%20technically%20has%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-has-gender-neutral-name-has-mixed-feelings-about-it-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egender-neutral%20name%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20admittedly%2C%20it%20wasn't%20an%20issue%20when%20we%20named%20him%20in%20Germany.%20That%20might%20be%20because%20the%20name%20is%20still%20predominantly%20used%20by%20males%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BLuca%26quot%3B%20situation.%20It's%20also%20possible%20that%20since%20it%20is%20a%20very%20unknown%20name%20in%20Germany%2C%20the%20naming%20authorities%20didn't%20even%20consider%20this%20possibility.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a58157d7-3b0e-4a30-b9af-82a570c4b2ee%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20brand%20names%2C%20titles%2C%20last%20names%2C%20or%20place%20names%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmerican%20kids%20sometimes%20sport%20unusual%20names%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeyonce-jay-z-family-photo-blue-ivy-tall-rumi-sir-2021-5%5C%22%20t