-of-violence-reported-from-some-lok-sabha-seats-during-polling%2Farticleshow%2F110414669.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cash%2C%20Kidnapping%3A%20How%20Pune%20Teen's%20Family%20Tried%20To%20Shift%20Blame%20After%20Crash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pune%20crash%2C%20where%20two%20techies%20were%20killed%20after%20being%20hit%20by%20a%20Porsche%2C%20has%20gripped%20the%20entire%20nation%20with%20the%20police%20investigation%20unveiling%20a%20new%20twist%20every%20day.%20Pune%20Police%20today%20revealed%20that%20the%20family%20of%20the%2017-year-old%20who%20was%20allegedly%20driving%20the%20car%20made%20efforts%20to%20pin%20the%20blame%20on%20a%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20engineers%20--%20Ashwini%20Kostha%20and%20Anish%20Awadhiya%20--%20were%20on%20the%20bike%20when%20the%20Porsche%2C%20being%20driven%20at%20200%20km%20per%20hour%2C%20hit%20their%20bike%20from%20behind.%20The%20two%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%20Police%20have%20said%20the%2017-year-old%20accused%2C%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20Pune%20realtor%2C%20was%20heavily%20drunk%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinutes%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20the%20teen's%20father%20called%20the%20driver%20and%20offered%20him%20a%20reward%20in%20lieu%20of%20a%20cash%20reward.%20They%20asked%20the%20driver%20to%20switch%20places%20with%20the%20boy%20and%20tell%20the%20police%20that%20he%20was%20driving%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20driver%20turned%20down%20the%20offer%2C%20they%20tried%20to%20threaten%20him%20into%20accepting%20that%20he%20was%20behind%20the%20wheel%20when%20the%20accident%20took%20place%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20teen's%20family%20driver%20was%20offered%20allurements%20and%20later%20threatened%20to%20take%20the%20blame%20for%20the%20Porsche%20crash%2C%26quot%3B%20Pune%20Police%20Commissioner%20Amitesh%20Kumar%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20has%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20where%20he%20also%20claims%20that%20the%20teen's%20grandfather%20locked%20him%20up%20and%20did%20not%20allow%20him%20to%20go%20home%20for%20two%20days.%20Police%20have%20registered%20a%20kidnapping%20case%20and%20arrested%20the%20grandfather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20teen's%20grandfather%20and%20father%20allegedly%20took%20the%20driver's%20phone%20and%20put%20him%20in%20confinement%20in%20his%20house%20on%20the%20premises%20of%20their%20bungalow%20from%20May%2019%20to%20May%2020.%20The%20driver%20was%20freed%20by%20his%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official%20from%20the%20crime%20branch%2C%20which%20is%20probing%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECops%20said%20that%20they%20have%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20other%20evidence%20to%20prove%20that%20the%20teen%2C%20who%20was%20drunk%2C%20was%20driving%20the%20Porsche.%20The%20boy%20had%20gone%20out%20to%20celebrate%20with%20his%20friends%20after%20passing%20his%20Class%2012%20board%20exams.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20partying%20at%20a%20posh%20Pune%20club%2C%20where%20they%20ran%20up%20a%20bill%20of%20Rs%2048%2C000%2C%20the%20boy%20fought%20with%20the%20driver%20for%20the%20keys%20of%20the%20car.%20The%20driver%20initially%20resisted%2C%20but%20allowed%20the%20teen%20to%20drive%20after%20a%20call%20with%20the%20boy's%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriving%20at%20200%20kmph%2C%20the%20teen%20crashed%20into%20a%20bike%20killing%20two%2024-year-old%20software%20engineers%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20He%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20by%20police%20at%203%20am%2C%20and%20granted%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20on%20the%20conditions%20seen%20as%20flimsy.%20He%20was%20asked%20to%20write%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20road%20accidents%2C%20told%20to%20work%20with%20traffic%20cops%20for%2015%20days%2C%20and%20seek%20counselling%20for%20his%20drinking%20habit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20later%20modified%20the%20order%20and%20sent%20him%20to%20a%20remand%20home%20till%20June%205.%20The%20police%20have%20requested%20the%20board%20permission%20to%20try%20the%20teen%20as%20an%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20sparked%20outrage%20across%20the%20nation%20with%20several%20protests%20being%20held%20seeking%20swift%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716624780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Feoj00p2o_pune-porsche-_625x300_22_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-cash-kidnapping-how-pune-teens-family-tried-to-shift-blame-after-crash-5742076%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pune%20crash%2C%20where%20two%20techies%20were%20killed%20after%20being%20hit%20by%20a%20Porsche%2C%20has%20gripped%20the%20entire%20nation%20with%20the%20police%20investigation%20unveiling%20a%20new%20twist%20every%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-cash-kidnapping-how-pune-teens-family-tried-to-shift-blame-after-crash-5742076%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-cash-kidnapping-how-pune-teens-family-tried-to-shift-blame-after-crash-5742076%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-cash-kidnapping-how-pune-teens-family-tried-to-shift-blame-after-crash-5742076%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20experts%20favour%20KKR%20for%20IPL%202024%20title%20over%20SRH%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716624704000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110417789%2Cimgsize-73596.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fwhy-former-cricketers-favour-kolkata-knight-riders-for-ipl-2024-title-over-sunrisers-hyderabad%2Farticleshow%2F110417668.cms%22%2C%22summary%2