After%20the%20accident%2C%20the%20driver%20was%20questioned%20at%20the%20police%20station.%20When%20the%20questioning%20was%20over%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20go%20home%2C%20but%20he%20(the%20teen's%20grandfather)%20forcibly%20took%20him%20to%20their%20home%2C%20snatched%20his%20phone%20and%20confined%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20cop%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20driver%2C%20said%20to%20be%20speeding%20at%20200%20km%20per%20hour%20after%20drinking%20heavily%2C%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20an%20observation%20home%20till%20June%205%20as%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20considers%20the%20police%20plea%20for%20permission%20to%20try%20him%20as%20an%20adult.%20The%20teen's%20father%2C%20a%20prominent%20realtor%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20under%20sections%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20engineers%20--%20Ashwini%20Kostha%20and%20Anish%20Awadhiya%20--%20were%20on%20the%20bike%20when%20the%20Porsche%20hit%20their%20bike%20from%20behind.%20They%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%20The%20boy%20was%20granted%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20of%20the%20accident%20on%20conditions%20seen%20as%20flimsy.%20He%20was%20asked%20to%20write%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20road%20accidents%2C%20told%20to%20work%20with%20traffic%20cops%20for%2015%20days%20and%20seek%20counselling%20for%20his%20drinking%20habit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20nationwide%20outrage%2C%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20later%20modified%20the%20order%20and%20sent%20him%20to%20the%20observation%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20allegations%20emerged%20that%20the%20influential%20family%20had%20tried%20to%20bend%20legal%20processes%20to%20shield%20the%20teen%2C%20an%20underworld%20link%20came%20to%20the%20fore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen's%20grandfather%20is%20an%20accused%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20murder%20case%20in%20connection%20with%20a%202009%20attack%20on%20a%20Shiv%20Sena%20corporator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CBI%20chargesheet%20filed%20in%20the%20case%