sition%20leaders%20to%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20spearheading%20an%20Opposition%20alliance%20of%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20parties%20competing%20jointly%20against%20PM%20Modi%2C%20including%20the%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20organisation%20grew%20out%20of%20an%20anti-corruption%20movement%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20and%20has%20been%20elected%20to%20office%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%2C%20but%20has%20struggled%20to%20establish%20itself%20as%20a%20nationwide%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20the%20authorities%20froze%20several%20Congress%20bank%20accounts%20as%20part%20of%20a%20running%20dispute%20over%20income%20tax%20returns%20filed%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20move%20the%20Gandhis%20said%20had%20severely%20impacted%20the%20party's%20ability%20to%20contest%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20no%20money%20to%20campaign%2C%20we%20cannot%20support%20our%20candidates%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20told%20reporters%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeatwave%20'Red%20Alert'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20voting%20in%20seven%20phases%20over%20six%20weeks%20to%20ease%20the%20immense%20logistical%20burden%20of%20staging%20an%20election%20in%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurnout%20is%20down%20several%20percentage%20points%20from%20the%20last%20national%20poll%20in%202019%2C%20with%20analysts%20blaming%20widespread%20expectations%20of%20a%20PM%20Modi%20victory%20as%20well%20as%20hotter-than-average%20temperatures%20heading%20into%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20weather%20bureau%20this%20week%20issued%20a%20heatwave%20%26quot%3Bred%20alert%26quot%3B%20for%20Delhi%20and%20surrounding%20states%20where%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20people%20were%20casting%20their%20ballots%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20warned%20of%20heightened%20health%20risks%