ass%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEx-Sarpanch%20Chhavi%20Rajawat%20has%20transformed%20the%20village%20of%20Soda%20into%20a%20space%20for%20development%2C%20education%20and%20change%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Chhavi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajawat%E2%80%99s%20stint%20as%20%3Cem%3Esarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20witnessed%20800%20households%20getting%20pipelines%2C%20around%20800%20homes%20getting%20toilets%2C%20numerous%20ponds%20being%20revived%2C%20and%20100%20roads%20being%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20when%20the%20villagers%20assumed%20the%20spate%20of%20development%20had%20reached%20its%20peak%2C%20Rajawat%20revived%20a%20defunct%20college%20and%20is%20already%20planning%20for%20a%20digital%20literacy%20centre.%20%E2%80%9CMiles%20to%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKnowledge%20does%20not%20discriminate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20Monday%20morning%20when%20I%20call%20Geeta%20(44).%20Her%20delayed%20response%2C%20as%20she%20explains%2C%20is%20because%20she%20is%20busy%20sketching%20out%20a%20curriculum%20for%20her%20Class%205%20students.%20It%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20year%20since%20Geeta%20has%20been%20working%20at%20this%20school.%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20the%20happiest%20I%20have%20ever%20been%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%20After%20being%20unemployed%20for%20years%2C%20she%20is%20relieved%20to%20have%20a%20well-paying%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Class%2012%2C%20Geeta%20quit%20her%20studies%20for%20five%20years.%20Her%20father%E2%80%99s%20untimely%20demise%20and%20her%20in-laws%E2%80%99%20unsupportive%20behaviour%20were%20the%20reasons.%20But%2C%20it%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20stepped%20in%20and%20motivated%20Geeta%20to%20take%20up%20studying%20once%20again%3B%20transferring%20Rs%203%2C000%20into%20her%20bank%20account%20and%20asking%20her%20to%20channel%20the%20money%20towards%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348078%2Fdelhi-constable-than-singh-ki-pathshala-teaches-underprivileged-children-for-free%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20at%20a%20construction%20site%20in%20Jaipur%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Geeta%20was%20forced%20to%20return%20to%20Soda%20in%202020.%20The%20dearth%20of%20work%20during%20the%20COVID%20lockdown%20made%20it%20impossible%20for%20her%20to%20continue.%20When%20she%20reached%20the%20village%2C%20news%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98new%E2%80%99%20college%20taking%20in%20applicants%20reached%20her.%20One%20conversation%20with%20Rajawat%20later%2C%20Geeta%20was%20convinced%20this%20was%20the%20place%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChhavi%20ma%E2%80%99am%20encouraged%20me%20to%20pursue%20my%20D%20El%20Ed%20(Diploma%20in%20Elementary%20Education).%20Everyone%20around%20me%20was%20keen%20to%20see%20me%20study.%20I%20began%20noticing%20how%20the%20village%20mindset%20had%20evolved.%E2%80%9D%20Geeta%20went%20on%20to%20complete%20the%20two-year%20course%20and%20secured%20a%20job%20at%20the%20village%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338824%2Fmuskaan-dreams-abhishek-dubey-introduces-technology-in-rural-school-education-digital-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimparting%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%2010-year-olds%20is%20her%20first%20priority%2C%20another%20goal%20is%20to%20dispel%20stereotypes%20that%20force%20women%20to%20sacrifice%20their%20dreams.%20Currently%2C%20there%20are%20550%20students%20at%20the%20college.%20They%20are%20engaged%20in%20one%20of%20the%20three%20courses%20offered%20here%3A%20BEd%20(Bachelor%20of%20Education)%2C%20a%20D%20El%20Ed%20(Diploma%20in%20Elementary%20Education)%2C%20and%20a%20BA%20(Bachelor%20of%20Arts)%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20